{"tid":2369582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唐樓爆炸起火 居民爬渠逃生","createTime":"2021-01-17T09:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T10:54:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4737cc5a0e0ebb1cad29b145b85cce35c57d8a","tid":2369582,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/3N4L227MAZGDFFBNWZWZQUS3MY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2F3N4L227MAZGDFFBNWZWZQUS3MY%2F&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=b835469f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210117%2F3N4L227MAZGDFFBNWZWZQUS3MY%2F&h=0e4f8875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210117/3N4L227MAZGDFFBNWZWZQUS3MY/</a><br />\n<br />\n唐樓爆炸起火 居民爬渠逃生<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深水埗鴨寮街唐樓單位昨清晨發生火警，更傳出爆炸聲，逾30名居民睡夢中驚醒逃生，九人吸入濃煙不適送院，有男街坊危急下爬水管落樓，有女街坊抱嬰兒送院，消防懷疑拖板電線短路引致火警。起火的1樓單位疑被改裝成民宿出租，嚴重焚毀，業主親友否認是民宿，並稱數月前出租單位予年輕人，據悉對方與另外兩三名青年同住。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九人不適送院<br />\n<br />\n起火單位約300呎，被燒至焦黑，隱約見到內有儲物櫃、兩張碌架床、一部健身單車及兩、三個啞鈴。居於樓上的鄧先生指，當時三名家人在家，包括兩名小童，家人皆留在單位等救援。火場毗鄰單位放置「太空艙」供住宿，有街坊懷疑起火單位經營民宿，鄧先生則指「星期六日假期係成日有年輕人嚟嘅，有啲嘈囉。」<br />\n<br />\n業主兩名親友否認經營民宿，指有青年。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n火警昨清晨5時許發生，大量火舌噴出窗外，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n居於3樓的任先生指，當時火勢猛烈，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SSHQ-QezdC4DfAq6KDQ0JKUJUzA=/886x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YASKSYS725GX7K6CFTQL4C3S34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSSHQ-QezdC4DfAq6KDQ0JKUJUzA%3D%2F886x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYASKSYS725GX7K6CFTQL4C3S34.jpg&h=8b6cae01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■深水埗唐樓單位昨清晨起火，濃煙直逼樓上多層。"},{"pid":"98a4f0a889092f74797b4a15ccb809ed824b0d29","tid":2369582,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:23:03.000Z","msg":"141?"},{"pid":"2c66941eb2b2b6d499ec4bac2f4efbbe7790cd76","tid":2369582,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"又係劏房亂劏搞到出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0bf5adeb0a9c90b52542c3da27b1e595d4f4ec","tid":2369582,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c66941eb2b2b6d499ec4bac2f4efbbe7790cd76","tid":2369582,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"又係劏房亂劏搞到出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:28:35.000Z","msg":"劏房波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f328379f898eaaf2d1766e76ee82fd0ee4b33099","tid":2369582,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"高溫消毒"},{"pid":"0cf37321454630773462e36e43b2c36b362c9726","tid":2369582,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"深水步真係笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12e7c5fcfdfd0d6a184011d65780a5fe152d483","tid":2369582,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"燒死班新移民同南亞狗啦"},{"pid":"9c3f701e1a4a87fc04e3a73040a84995680a3604","tid":2369582,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a12e7c5fcfdfd0d6a184011d65780a5fe152d483","tid":2369582,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:35:17.000Z","msg":"燒死班新移民同南亞狗啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:48:11.000Z","msg":"都好多單身撚租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b39d5c9bee1dace86a8326031667197f926d19","tid":2369582,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c3f701e1a4a87fc04e3a73040a8499568